%h1 Listing pitches

%table
  %tr
    %th Country
    %th Min
    %th Max
    %th Expertise
    %th Status
    %th

  - @pitches.each do |pitch|
    %tr
      %td= pitch.holiday.country.name
      %td= pitch.min
      %td= pitch.max
      %td= pitch.expertise
